---
permalink: "/_admin/index.html"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
  <title>DK App Tools Admin CMS</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #08090a;
      --bg-2: #101216;
      --panel: rgba(24, 26, 30, 0.94);
      --panel-2: rgba(31, 34, 39, 0.86);
      --panel-3: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
      --border: rgba(220, 174, 75, 0.24);
      --border-soft: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
      --gold: #d6a83d;
      --gold-2: #f0cf77;
      --gold-soft: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.14);
      --text: #f4efe6;
      --muted: #aaa59a;
      --muted-2: #7f7a70;
      --safe: #7bd88f;
      --warn: #f0cf77;
      --danger: #ff7a7a;
      --info: #8bb9ff;
      --shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.16), transparent 34rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(139, 185, 255, 0.08), transparent 28rem),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.08), transparent 30rem),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg), var(--bg-2) 55%, #070809);
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.24;
      background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.42) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 24px 24px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black, transparent 86%);
    }

    button {
      font: inherit;
    }

    .shell {
      position: relative;
      width: min(1280px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 26px 0 46px;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .mark {
      display: grid;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      place-items: center;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 15px;
      color: var(--gold-2);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.2), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035));
      box-shadow: 0 18px 70px rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.13);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .brand-subtitle {
      margin-top: 2px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .top-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 13px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .pill.safe {
      border-color: rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.28);
      color: var(--safe);
      background: rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.08);
    }

    .pill.warn {
      border-color: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.26);
      color: var(--gold-2);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.09);
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.12fr 0.88fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(30, 33, 38, 0.94), rgba(18, 20, 23, 0.94));
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-main {
      padding: 30px;
      border-color: var(--border);
      min-height: 310px;
    }

    .kicker {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 780px;
      font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 72px);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
    }

    .lead {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 26px;
    }

    .metric {
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.032);
    }

    .metric-number {
      color: var(--gold-2);
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }

    .metric-label {
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .side-panel {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .status-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .status-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 13px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .status-list strong {
      color: var(--text);
      text-align: right;
    }

    .notice {
      padding: 16px 17px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.24);
      border-radius: 19px;
      background: var(--gold-soft);
      color: #f6e4b2;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .rail {
      position: sticky;
      top: 18px;
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .rail-title {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .nav-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 12px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 15px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .nav-item.active {
      border-color: var(--border);
      color: var(--gold-2);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.1);
    }

    .nav-icon {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 9px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .main-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    }

    .section p {
      margin: 7px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .button-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 9px;
    }

    .button {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 11px 13px;
      color: var(--gold-2);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.08);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .button.secondary {
      border-color: var(--border-soft);
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
    }

    .button[disabled] {
      cursor: not-allowed;
      opacity: 0.5;
      filter: grayscale(0.25);
    }

    .module-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .module {
      min-height: 160px;
      padding: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.027);
    }

    .module-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .module-icon {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    }

    .module-state {
      padding: 6px 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 950;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .module-state.ready {
      color: var(--safe);
      background: rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.08);
    }

    .module-state.mock {
      color: var(--gold-2);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.1);
    }

    .module-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .module-text {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .table {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 17px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.026);
    }

    .row-title {
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .row-meta {
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--gold-2);
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.12);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 950;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .badge.safe {
      color: var(--safe);
      background: rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.08);
    }

    .badge.info {
      color: var(--info);
      background: rgba(139, 185, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .editor-mock {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .field {
      padding: 13px 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 15px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .preview-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.1), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025)),
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .preview-image {
      height: 140px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 16px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 25% 20%, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.24), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15));
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .health-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .health-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 12px 13px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      border-radius: 15px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.024);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--muted-2);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    }

    .dot.safe {
      background: var(--safe);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(123, 216, 143, 0.09);
    }

    .dot.warn {
      background: var(--warn);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.09);
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 22px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1040px) {
      .hero,
      .layout,
      .split {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .rail {
        position: static;
      }

      .module-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 680px) {
      .shell {
        width: min(100% - 22px, 1280px);
        padding-top: 16px;
      }

      .topbar,
      .section-header {
        align-items: flex-start;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .top-actions {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }

      .hero-main,
      .section,
      .side-panel,
      .rail {
        padding: 18px;
        border-radius: 22px;
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .module-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="shell">
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="mark">DK</div>
        <div>
          <div class="brand-title">DK App Tools CMS</div>
          <div class="brand-subtitle">Защитен контролен център за сайта</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="top-actions">
        <div class="pill safe">Cloudflare Access active</div>
        <div class="pill warn">Mock/read-only mode</div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="card hero-main">
        <div class="kicker">Protected CMS dashboard</div>
        <h1>Управление на целия DK App Tools сайт.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Това е първият dashboard mock на бъдещата CMS система. Целта е съдържанието,
          app страниците, снимките, preview-тата и publish процесът да се управляват оттук,
          без ръчно редактиране на код за всяка малка промяна.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-number">3</div>
            <div class="metric-label">published articles</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-number">1</div>
            <div class="metric-label">active app page</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-number">0</div>
            <div class="metric-label">write operations enabled</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="card side-panel">
        <div>
          <div class="kicker">System state</div>
          <ul class="status-list">
            <li><span>Admin host</span><strong>admin.dkapptools.com</strong></li>
            <li><span>Access layer</span><strong>Cloudflare Access</strong></li>
            <li><span>Write backend</span><strong>Not connected</strong></li>
            <li><span>Publish action</span><strong>Disabled</strong></li>
            <li><span>GitHub token</span><strong>Not in browser</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="notice">
          Safe rule: CMS UI може да изглежда реално, но Save Draft, Publish, Upload и Maintenance writes
          остават disabled, докато няма защитен server-side backend.
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="layout">
      <aside class="card rail">
        <div class="rail-title">CMS Sections</div>
        <nav class="nav-list" aria-label="CMS sections">
          <div class="nav-item active"><span class="nav-icon">⌂</span>Dashboard</div>
          <div class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">✎</span>Articles</div>
          <div class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">▣</span>Apps</div>
          <div class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">◉</span>Media</div>
          <div class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">?</span>Support</div>
          <div class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">§</span>Privacy</div>
          <div class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">✓</span>Site Health</div>
          <div class="nav-item"><span class="nav-icon">↗</span>Deploy</div>
        </nav>
      </aside>

      <div class="main-grid">
        <section class="card section">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2>CMS modules</h2>
              <p>Основните области, които admin панелът постепенно ще започне да управлява.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="button-row">
              <button class="button secondary" disabled>Refresh checks</button>
              <button class="button" disabled>Open live editor</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="module-grid">
            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">✎</div>
                <span class="module-state mock">Mock</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">Articles Studio</h3>
              <p class="module-text">Чернови, structured blocks, card image, preview и publish workflow.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">▣</div>
                <span class="module-state mock">Mock</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">App Pages</h3>
              <p class="module-text">Product pages, Google Play links, feature cards, changelog и screenshots.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">◉</div>
                <span class="module-state mock">Mock</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">Media Library</h3>
              <p class="module-text">Image dimensions, alt text, usage tracking и low-resolution warnings.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">?</div>
                <span class="module-state mock">Mock</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">Support / FAQ</h3>
              <p class="module-text">Поддръжка, често задавани въпроси и app-specific help content.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">§</div>
                <span class="module-state mock">Mock</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">Privacy / Legal</h3>
              <p class="module-text">Privacy pages, last updated dates, policy checks и data safety notes.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">✓</div>
                <span class="module-state ready">Ready idea</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">Site Health</h3>
              <p class="module-text">Missing metadata, broken links, image quality и build-risk checks.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="split">
          <div class="card section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <div>
                <h2>Articles queue</h2>
                <p>Примерен списък със статии и бъдещ draft/publish статус.</p>
              </div>
              <button class="button" disabled>New article</button>
            </div>

            <div class="table">
              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Why offline-first security still matters</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Article • Published • Card image OK</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge safe">Published</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">How local file vaults protect privacy</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Article • Published • Metadata OK</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge safe">Published</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Нова статия за бъдещия редактор</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Draft mock • Needs preview • Backend not connected</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Draft mock</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <div>
                <h2>Editor preview</h2>
                <p>Бъдещ structured editor вместо ръчно пипане на markdown/code.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="button-row">
                <button class="button secondary" disabled>Save draft</button>
                <button class="button" disabled>Publish</button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="editor-mock">
              <div class="field">Title: Нова статия за Offline FileSecure</div>
              <div class="field">Slug: offline-filesecure-secure-local-vault</div>
              <div class="field">Card image: required • alt text required</div>
              <div class="field">Blocks: heading, paragraph, image figure, callout</div>
              <div class="preview-card">
                <div class="preview-image"></div>
                <div class="row-title">Article card preview</div>
                <div class="row-meta">
                  Тук CMS-ът ще показва как статията ще изглежда в Articles, Search и public article page.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="split">
          <div class="card section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <div>
                <h2>Site health checks</h2>
                <p>Mock проверки, които по-късно ще пазят сайта от счупено съдържание.</p>
              </div>
              <span class="badge info">Mock status</span>
            </div>

            <div class="health-list">
              <div class="health-item"><span>Missing article descriptions</span><span class="dot safe"></span></div>
              <div class="health-item"><span>Missing image alt text</span><span class="dot safe"></span></div>
              <div class="health-item"><span>Low-resolution card images</span><span class="dot warn"></span></div>
              <div class="health-item"><span>Broken internal links</span><span class="dot safe"></span></div>
              <div class="health-item"><span>Maintenance mode accidentally on</span><span class="dot safe"></span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <div>
                <h2>Deploy pipeline</h2>
                <p>Бъдещият publish flow ще показва commit/deploy/live статус.</p>
              </div>
              <span class="badge">Read-only</span>
            </div>

            <div class="table">
              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">GitHub commit</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Disabled until protected backend exists</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Blocked</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Cloudflare Pages deploy</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Will run after safe backend commit</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge info">Planned</span>
              </div>

              <div class="row">
                <div>
                  <div class="row-title">Public content live</div>
                  <div class="row-meta">Only after successful deploy confirmation</div>
                </div>
                <span class="badge info">Planned</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card section">
          <div class="section-header">
            <div>
              <h2>Safety guardrails</h2>
              <p>Тези правила остават активни, докато CMS-ът няма реален protected write backend.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="module-grid">
            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">🔒</div>
                <span class="module-state ready">Required</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">No browser secrets</h3>
              <p class="module-text">GitHub token, deploy token и private API secrets никога не се изпращат към browser-а.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">⛔</div>
                <span class="module-state ready">Required</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">Writes disabled</h3>
              <p class="module-text">Save Draft, Publish, Upload и Maintenance writes остават disabled в mock режима.</p>
            </article>

            <article class="module">
              <div class="module-top">
                <div class="module-icon">✓</div>
                <span class="module-state ready">Required</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="module-title">Preview before publish</h3>
              <p class="module-text">Публично съдържание се пуска само след preview, validation, backend commit и успешен deploy.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      DK App Tools CMS • Protected mock UI • Cloudflare Access protected • No write operations enabled
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
